Note on academic attribution:

This code implements the algorithm described in:

  Naqvi, N., Rehman, S. U., & Islam, M. Z. (2023).
  WinDrift++: A diversified detector for concept drift.
  IEEE Transactions on Artificial Intelligence.

The software licence above covers this implementation only. All rights to the
original algorithm, methodology, and experimental design belong to the
original authors. Please cite the paper if you use this implementation in
academic or research work.
